# PR-X apply-request channel.
#
# Bind-mounted into acc-tui at /app/.acc-apply.  The TUI writes
# workspace.request here when the operator picks a working directory;
# the host-side scripts/acc-apply-watcher.sh reads it and runs
# `acc-deploy.sh apply-workspace <host_path>` to recreate the agents
# onto that directory.  Runtime files (workspace.request / .status /
# watcher.log / watcher.pid) are git-ignored; this .gitkeep just
# guarantees the mount source exists on a clean checkout.
